entries.femaleVariant: Ooh, we're lookin' pale today. Hangover?
Nah, just couldn't sleep. Again with the screaming, the shouting, the fighting...
Yeah, typical. Listen, get me some more of those stones, will ya? Pay by the piece.
OK, but... The hell you need all those rocks for?
Hah, wow. Maybe you should shove 'em up your ass, grab the bad vibes there, too.
Hey, relax. Look, I got a regular client. Corpo in a stiff suit.
Heh heh, what a gonk. Guess he earned it though. Anyway, see if you can get me somethin' off him too.
Find your own rich gonk. Can grab one at random. Guarantee they're all fucked in the head in some way.
Gonna live to see tomorrow only thanks to my magic stones and his sealed windows. Faith works miracles, tellin' ya.
